#

Kung Pao Shrimp with Crunchy Vegetables

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishPeanuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

ChineseAsian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Stir-FryQuick MealSpicyAsian Cuisine

Description

A quick and flavorful stir-fry featuring succulent shrimp, vibrant vegetables, and a spicy sauce.

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • bell pepper (diced): 1
  • zucchini (sliced): 1
  • carrot (sliced): 1
  • green onion (chopped): 2
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • peanut butter: 2 tablespoons
  • rice vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • sesame oil: 1 tablespoon
  • red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon (to taste)
  • roasted peanuts (for garnish): 1/4 cup
  • cooked rice (for serving): 2 cups
